## Special Instructions

- ILIELEKEZA (Directive, mandatory) vs ILISHAURIWA (Recommendation, optional): Both must be tracked and logged.
- Resolution status flow: open, in-progress, completed, overdue, archived.
- MinuteHub integration: All endpoints/events must support webhook sync and audit sharing.

